title: Aggie cornerback Will Lee III intent on redemption as season rolls on | TexAgs
text: [Texas A&M Football](/aggie-football) Aggie cornerback Will Lee III intent on redemption as season rolls on September 5, 2024 3,042 With nine tackles and a pass breakup against Notre Dame, cornerback Will Lee III has an impressive Texas A&M debut in front of the 12th Man. In an exclusive interview, "The Blanket" spoke about his first game in Aggieland and what the Maroon & White aim to do vs. McNeese. Never miss the latest news from TexAgs! Join our free email list
